document.contentSummaryTitle: 10 of Food magazine’s all-time favourite desserts
document.contentSummary: As we embark on the hunt for New Zealand's dessert queen or king, we look back on some of our favourite sweet treats from the past couple of years.
document.pageTitle: 10 of Food magazine’s all-time favourite desserts
document.pageMetaDescription: As we embark on the hunt for New Zealand's dessert queen or king, we look back on some of our favourite sweet treats from the past couple of years.
document.contentBody: [{"type":"paragraph","label":"Paragraph","content":"As we embark on the hunt for New Zealand's dessert queen or king, we take a look back on some of our favourite sweet treats from the past couple of years. From our classic white chocolate and raspberry cheesecake to our newly celebrated vegan-friendly date mousse, these recipes prove that there's no hard and fast rule to creating the perfect dessert! \n\nDon't forget to [enter to your own dessert recipe](http://www.foodtolove.co.nz/food-magazine-best-dessert-38147|target=\"_blank\") to win the title of New Zealand's Best Dessert Cook, along with $2000 in prizes."}]
